	<bean id="toolsConnectToken" class="com.fortify.manager.security.ws.AuthenticationTokenSpec">
		<property name="key" value="ToolsConnectToken"/>
		<property name="capabilityDescription">
			<value>
				<![CDATA[
				Use this token with the Fortify Static Code Analyzer applications (including Audit Workbench, IDE plugins, and utilities)
				that connect to Software Security Center for collaborative auditing, remediation, and uploading of scan results.
				WARNING: Due to the access this token provides and its maximum allowed lifetime, you must take extra care securing the token to reduce risk of API misuse or unintended use.
				It is highly recommended that you evaluate the planned use of this token and ensure you limit the life of the token based on your environments' tolerance for risk.
				]]>
